### Location
https://doc.rust-lang.org/beta/nightly-rustc/rustc_hir/enum.ExprKind.html#variant.MethodCall
https://doc.rust-lang.org/beta/nightly-rustc/rustc_hir/enum.QPath.html

### Summary
Not found on some of the method link under `rustc_hir/enum` page, for example,  `type_dependent_def_id` on [rustc_hir/enum.ExprKind](https://doc.rust-lang.org/beta/nightly-rustc/rustc_hir/enum.ExprKind.html#variant.MethodCall) 
 
 but it's available under 
 
 [rustc_hir/hir/enum.ExprKind](https://doc.rust-lang.org/beta/nightly-rustc/rustc_hir/hir/enum.ExprKind.html#variant.MethodCall).
